other_tests.findings: Limited mobility of mitral valve leaflets in the four-chamber view, all chordae inserted into the posteromedial PM, detection of coarctation of the aorta and a small left ventricle.

All chordae connected to elongated posteromedial PM with narrowing of interchordal spaces and decreased diameter at mitral valve opening. Anterolateral PM attached to the ventricular wall for its entire length.
